#15314
Firebrandt~
Firebrandt~
An injured adventurer is laying here, probably has been for some time now.
~
He looks to be not too old at all, but obviously someone who has done his share
of adventuring and has probably slayed a monster or two in the process.
He half lays, half sits up against a far wall, with visible wounds covering
the better part of him, though one in particular looks bad: His leg looks to
be gashed open just at the knee.  A crude splint fashioned from a slightly used
torch and some torn cloth holds it together, but you can tell there is no
way he's going to make it out of here with such damage.
~
