> greet_prog 100~
if ispc($n)
if position($i) == 6
groan
'Help me, whoever you are...  I've broken my leg and cannot stand on it to leave this place.  Please heal my wounds, for I shall be in your debt.
endif
endif
~
> fight_prog 75~
mpecho Firebrandt clinches his teeth in pain as he steps onto his broken leg during the fight.
mpat puff mpforce puff mpdamage firebrandt 10
~
> act_prog p A warm feeling fills your body.~
if position($i) != 6
'Thank you, but I think I'm fine now.  I believe I can even walk.
else
stand
'Thank you, truly I owe you my life now.  I wish I had more to give you, but this is all I have on me that might be of any help to you, you can have it.
mpoload 15304 1
give crowbar $n
'I was trying to find a way to open this door, when I was jumped by 10 red ants simultaneously.  I managed to take a couple of them down, but they backed me all the way up to this dead end.  Once they wounded me, they left me for dead.
'All I can tell you is that I've heard that the key to this door is somewhere down in these sewers, though it must be hidden because I haven't been able to find it.  Hopefully you'll have better luck.
endif
~
> act_prog p gives you antidote.~
if position($i) != 6
'Thank you, but I'm fine now and don't need anything more.
else
'hmm..antidote..this would work if I was poisoned, but I'm not.  I'll need something other then this.
endif
give antidote $n
~
> act_prog p gives you a red potion.~
if position($i) != 6
'Thank you, but I think I'm fine now.  I believe I can even walk.
give 'red potion' $n
else
quaff 'red potion'
mpecho Firebrandt quaffs a red potion.
stand
'Thank you, truly I owe you my life now.  I wish I had more to give you, but this is all I have on me that might be of any help to you, you can have it.
mpoload 15304 1
give crowbar $n
'I was trying to find a way to open this door, when I was jumped by 10 red ants simultaneously.  I managed to take a couple of them down, but they backed me all the way up to this dead end.  Once they wounded me, they left me for dead.
'All I can tell you is that I've heard that the key to this door is somewhere down in these sewers, though it must be hidden because I haven't been able to find it.  Hopefully you'll have better luck.
endif
~
> act_prog p gives you~
'Hmm, it doesn't look I can really use this item, thanks anyways...
drop all
~
