#15301
Underground Sewers~
The light down here is very dim, or rather lack thereof.  Some light trails in
from above, but otherwise it is totally pitch black down here, so artificial
light is a must.  The floor is wet dirt, mud in most places, and the walls are
made of large old bricks.  The roof curves in an arch and continues on to the
north like a tunnel.
~
